org.gradoop.storage.hbase.impl.api

Interface GraphElementHandler

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ElementHandler, Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    EdgeHandler, VertexHandler
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HBaseEdgeHandler, HBaseGraphElementHandler, HBaseVertexHandler

    public interface GraphElementHandler
extends ElementHandler
    Responsible for reading and writing graph element entity data from and to HBase. These are usually vertex and edge data objects.
